(35, 'Management of paracetamol poisoning', 'Paracetamol (acetaminophen) is an effective oral analgesic, with few adverse effects when used at the recommended dose. Nevertheless, paracetamol poisoning is common and potentially fatal...', 4, '2013-09-26 09:53:39', 0, NULL, NULL),
